Determine whether this social media post from Donald Trump contains a personal insult to Kamala Harris's intelligence. Simply return "yes" or "no".
content: RT @TeamTrumpGround zero for the outbreak of anti-Jewish hate under Kamala Harris has been our college campuses. Kamala Harris said that the radical demonstrators on college campuses were showing what “human emotion should be.” This message is wrong—it is dangerous—and it is unbefitting a candidate for president of the United States.
